text: Avocet is the common name of a genus of wading birds, Recurvirostra. Avocet may also refer to: *Avocet snipe eel, a fish *Avro Avocet, a 1920s British naval fighter aircraft prototype *Avocet Mining, a West African company *Avocet (album), by Bert Jansch *USS Avocet (AVP-4), a 1918-1946 US Navy minesweeper *USS Avocet (AMCU-16), a 1953-1960 US Navy minesweeper * Avocet, a 1986 prototype locomotive of the British Rail Class 89
title: Avocet (disambiguation)
